---
title: Cheesy Pork & Bacon Cornish-Style Pasties with Apple Salad & Tomato Relish
description: This pastry delight brings all the warmth and comfort of a pie into a fun handheld meal! Packed with succulent pork, golden nuggets of bacon, and a hearty mix of veggies, this flaky masterpiece is a winner in our eyes!
